trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>mpns</languageKeyword> object is used to send push notifications to Windows Phone 8 and Windows Phone 8.1 Silverlight apps.
trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>mpns</languageKeyword> object is used to send push notifications to Windows Phone 8 and Windows Phone 8.1 Silverlight apps.

trans-unit.source: To send push notifications to a Windows Phone Store 8.1 app, you must use the <link xlink:href="91200cf1-66af-43fb-bc7f-31d17cb76607" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">wns object</link>.
trans-unit.target: To send push notifications to a Windows Phone Store 8.1 app, you must use the <link xlink:href="91200cf1-66af-43fb-bc7f-31d17cb76607" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">wns object</link>.

trans-unit.source: MPNS is not supported by Notification Hubs for Windows Phone Store 8.1 apps.
trans-unit.target: MPNS is not supported by Notification Hubs for Windows Phone Store 8.1 apps.

trans-unit.source: For an example of how to send push notifications from your mobile service to a Windows Phone 8 app, see <externalLink><linkText>Add push notifications to your Mobile Services app</linkText><linkUri>http://azure.microsoft.com/documentation/articles/mobile-services-javascript-backend-windows-phone-get-started-push/</linkUri></externalLink>.
trans-unit.target: For an example of how to send push notifications from your mobile service to a Windows Phone 8 app, see <externalLink><linkText>Add push notifications to your Mobile Services app</linkText><linkUri>http://azure.microsoft.com/documentation/articles/mobile-services-javascript-backend-windows-phone-get-started-push/</linkUri></externalLink>.

trans-unit.source: <token>nextref_zumo</token> doesn’t require you to register your app with MPNS to enable authenticated usage.
trans-unit.target: <token>nextref_zumo</token> doesn’t require you to register your app with MPNS to enable authenticated usage.

trans-unit.source: Because of this, you cannot send more than 500 messages per user each day by using MPNS.
trans-unit.target: Because of this, you cannot send more than 500 messages per user each day by using MPNS.
